{
  "chapter": 3,
  "chapter_summary": "第三回\"历尽沧桑\"讲述裴珏从飞龙镖局越墙出走后，在北京城中流浪的经历。他身无分文，饥肠辘辘，却被一个猥琐汉子以\"拍花\"迷药拐入\"像姑团子\"（男色妓院）。裴珏被换上女装，险遭胖嫖客凌辱，幸而胖嫖客用清水喷醒了他。裴珏清醒后奋力反抗，痛打胖子，但引来两个彪形打手。他情急之下跳窗逃出，衣衫不整地流落城郊。入夜后又遭一群流氓地痞围堵，误认他为女子欲行不轨。危急时刻，一位骑纯白骏马的白衣书生出现，以精妙的鞭法点穴功夫击退众流氓。书生见裴珏无家可归，主动提出收留他并传授武功。裴珏欣然同意，随书生而去。本章奠定了裴珏流浪江湖的起点，白马书生的出场为其后续成长埋下伏笔。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "众女人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这货色真不坏。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 65
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_xing_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "一名女子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们看，这货色的皮肤真嫩，脸蛋儿像吹弹得破似的，打扮起来，包管像是女的。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_suo_han_zi",
      "speaker_name": "猥琐汉子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我上楼去替他打扮打扮。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 73
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pang_piao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "胖子",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "小乖乖，不用怕，来——",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 103
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pang_piao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "胖子",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "小乖乖，你要干什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 105
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pang_piao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "胖子",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "小臭货，你疯了。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pang_piao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "胖子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快救命呀！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 111
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_shou_a",
      "speaker_name": "打手",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "小兔崽子，敢情你活得有点不耐烦了！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 123
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_shou_a",
      "speaker_name": "打手",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "小兔崽子，你也不打听打听这里是什么地方，就在这儿作死！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_shou_a",
      "speaker_name": "打手",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "今天大爷非好好治治你。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 135
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_mang_di_pi",
      "speaker_name": "流氓地痞",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "这几天正没钱，又闷得慌，这小妞儿真是天上送来的宝货。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_mang_di_pi",
      "speaker_name": "地痞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有人来了。",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 205
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_mang_di_pi",
      "speaker_name": "地痞",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "你再叫大爷就宰了你。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 209
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_mang_di_pi",
      "speaker_name": "地痞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有人闯来，大爷们就一块儿作翻了他。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 215
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_ma_shu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "白马书生",
      "listener": "char_liu_mang_di_pi",
      "text": "你们是谁？在这里干什么？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 219
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_mang_di_pi",
      "speaker_name": "地痞",
      "listener": "char_bai_ma_shu_sheng",
      "text": "你小子是什么玩意儿，竟敢来管大爷的闲事，趁早夹着尾巴——",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 223
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_mang_di_pi",
      "speaker_name": "地痞",
      "listener": "char_bai_ma_shu_sheng",
      "text": "好小子，你敢打人。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_mang_di_pi",
      "speaker_name": "地痞",
      "listener": "char_bai_ma_shu_sheng",
      "text": "好，你打，你打。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 233
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_mang_di_pi",
      "speaker_name": "地痞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "杀人啦。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_ma_shu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "白马书生",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "你的家在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_ma_shu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "白马书生",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "你没有家吗？怎地不说话？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 257
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_ma_shu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "白马书生",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "喂，女孩子，快回来。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 265
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_ma_shu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "白马书生",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "你既然没有家，要不要跟着我走？我也是个没有家的人。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 277
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_ma_shu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "白马书生",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "我还可以传些武功给你，让你不受别人欺负，至于你能学得了多少，那就要看你自己了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 281
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_jue",
      "speaker_name": "裴珏",
      "listener": "char_bai_ma_shu_sheng",
      "text": "可是我太笨，学来学去总是学不好。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 287
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_ma_shu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "白马书生",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "你学过武功？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_ma_shu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "白马书生",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "谁说你笨？你以前跟谁学过武功的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_jue",
      "speaker_name": "裴珏",
      "listener": "char_bai_ma_shu_sheng",
      "text": "龙形八掌檀明。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_ma_shu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "白马书生",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "他算什么东西！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_ma_shu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "白马书生",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "你跟不跟我一齐走？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 303
    }
  ],
